b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":2518,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"Dragalia Life #400, Now Available![Update]","message":"<div>[Updated <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1640930400\\"><\/span>]<br>Thank you for participating in the surveys about your favorite comic panels! The three panels that were selected in the surveys have been implemented as in-game stickers.<br><br>To see the new stickers, select Player Info under Menu at the top of the screen in-game, then select Stickers and see the Available Stickers section. If you want to use the new stickers, please edit your Sticker Loadout, which is also under Stickers.<\/div><hr><div><br><\/div><div>Issue #400 of the comic strip Dragalia Life is now available!<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>To view the Dragalia Life comics in-game, tap Dragalia Life from the menu at the top of the screen. To view them on the official website, select the Dragalia Life banner on the main page.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>We&#39;re planning on holding a series of surveys to celebrate the release of issue #400.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>We will be conducting surveys with three different themes to find your favorite Dragalia Life comic panel from issues 301-400. The responses on the official Dragalia Lost Twitter accounts listed below will be tallied, and the comic panels with the most votes for each of the themes will be implemented as stickers that can be used in-game.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25bcSurvey medium<\/div><div>\\u30fbOfficial English Dragalia Lost Twitter account (@DragaliaLostApp)<\/div><div>\\u30fbOfficial Japanese Dragalia Lost Twitter account(@dragalialost)<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25bcSurvey themes and duration<\/div><div>\\u30fbTheme 1: Shock and Awe<\/div><div>\\u30fbTheme 2: Par Excellence<\/div><div>\\u30fbTheme 3: Emotion Commotion<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Duration: <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1634277600\\"><\/span> to <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1634450400\\"><\/span><\/div><div>Note: Dates and times are approximate.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25bcSurvey content<\/div><div>The surveys will be posted on the official Dragalia Lost social media accounts around <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1634277600\\"><\/span>. Respond to the survey tweets and cast your votes!<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25bcSurvey results<\/div><div>The survey results will be posted on the official Dragalia Lost social media accounts around <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1634623200\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>The stickers will be implemented and will be added directly to your Available Stickers at that time. This notification will be updated once they have been added.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1634277600,"prev_article_id":"2735","next_article_id":"2711","image_path":"","update_time":1640930370}}}'